{"tid":281743,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 食食吓麵包入面有頭髮 無錯係入面...","createTime":"2017-06-13T01:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T05:05:50.000Z","uid":122514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5efa4bdb06e0843a8542932ac58df2a8cb62238d","tid":281743,"uid":122514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"琴日先讚完A1好食 於是去咗買早餐<br />\n食食吓有條頭髮係入面<br />\n心諗 無事嘅可能係自己啲頭髮啫<br />\n望真啲 咦黑色嘅我金毛嚟㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算 頭髮啫嚇我唔到嘅 諗住拎走條頭髮照食<br />\n屌拎唔起痴實咗個包嘅<br />\n即係搓粉個時已經係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴絲打應該點做好<br />\nps已keep好證據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/092933_2109fd65c4db0caa02ae3505fb7085c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F092933_2109fd65c4db0caa02ae3505fb7085c4.jpg&h=c1bd67e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"117b7be1bc1ebfdac3f5b1a574a073bb36bb7730","tid":281743,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:40:42.000Z","msg":"係頭髮算好彩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de28faa1d8ca84d70c593bb4fd22203fc7578da","tid":281743,"uid":12712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"成鳩日出去食野都有頭髪架啦"},{"pid":"9ec43485881b21d7875b412526d3144958539be0","tid":281743,"uid":108568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係頭髮算好彩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鳩毛拉番直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15708e79fd13292645a1be92347962bbe5f61439","tid":281743,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:45:58.000Z","msg":"咁撚煩膠就咪撚出去食啦